description: REAL (Real Estate Asset Ledger) is a new Ethereum Smart-Contracts governed ecosystem that applies Blockchain technologies to the enormous Real Estate investment industry. Key to our ecosystem is the innovation of REAL Tokens, a unique Blockchain-secured digital asset with inherent value as a secure cryptocurrency, which may be traded or used to participate in Crowdfunding by purchasing Real Estate Participations (RPP) on our platform.
name: REAL
